item.description:
This meetup is for _advanced players only_. I'll set up nets ~ 6pm and we'll play til it gets dark.

See http://volleyball.mee... for details of levels. Briefly, if you aren't comfortable with 5-1 or 6-2, if you aren't comfortable hitting or setting 2s, shoots, or the occasional 1, this is probably not the level for you. In order to maintain a quality game, you may be asked to leave if your level of play is not sufficient.

As of now the weather outlook seems ok. If that changes drastically, I'll send out an update.

Seeya tomorrow...

-Ted
item.name: ADVANCED Outdoor Volleyball 6pm Weds 6/24 @ Sydney & Pacific
